/-- The natural map between `⨁ (i : Σ i, α i), δ i.1 i.2` and `⨁ i (j : α i), δ i j`.-/
noncomputable def sigmaCurry : (⨁ i : Σi, _, δ i.1 i.2) →+ ⨁ (i) (j), δ i j where
